 <name>PHP_CodeSniffer_Standards_RoundCube</name>
 <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
 <summary>PHP_CodeSniffer_Standards_RoundCube implements the PEAR CS and makes a few additions.</summary>
 <description>Based on the PEAR CS, PHP_CodeSniffer_Standards_RoundCube is used to check the coding style used on the RoundCube webmail project.
 </description>
